origin":18521,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Jannah: Believers enter Paradise as young, beautiful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 8, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe people of Paradise will enter Paradise with smooth and hairless skin, kohl upon their eyes, at thirty or thirty-three years of age.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2545 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0630\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u062c\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6174,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/09\/best-food-earned-hard-work\/","url_meta":{"origin":18521,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Independence: Best food to eat earned by hard work","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 9, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the most wholesome food a man can eat is that which he has earned.\" Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 4397 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0623\u064e\u0637\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0628\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0627 \u0623\u064e\u0643\u064e\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13102,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/24\/women-gold-silk-halal\/","url_meta":{"origin":18521,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Clothing: Women can wear gold and silk, not men","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah Almighty has made lawful silk and gold for the women of my nation, but he has forbidden them for men.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 5265 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0645\u064f\u0648\u0633\u064e\u0649 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":5677,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/29\/mention-name-of-allah-eat\/","url_meta":{"origin":18521,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Meat: Assume meat of the believers is Halal","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 29, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Some people among the bedouins would bring us meat and we did not know if the name of Allah was mentioned over it or not. The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cMention the name of Allah over it and eat.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304\u2026","rel":"","context":"I